<h3>Custom controls</h3>
<p>You can play, pause, mute and unmute the component from the surrounding controller. Try changing the values below:</p>

<section>
	YouTube ID: {{input value=youTubeId}}<br>
	Volume: {{input type="number" value=volume}}<br>
	<br>
	<button {{action "togglePlay" target=emberYoutube}}>
		{{if emberYoutube.isPlaying "Pause" "Play"}}
	</button>
	<button {{action "toggleVolume" target=emberYoutube}}>
		{{if emberYoutube.isMuted "Unmute" "Mute"}}
	</button>
	<button {{action "seekTo" 90 target=emberYoutube}}>
		Seek to 01:30
	</button>
</section>

<hr>

<section>
	<h3>The player</h3>
	{{ember-youtube
		ytid=youTubeId
		volume=volume
		playerVars=customPlayerVars
		showControls=false
		showProgress=true
		showDebug=true
		lazyload=false

		delegate=this
		delegate-as="emberYoutube"

		playing=(action "ytPlaying")
		paused=(action "ytPaused")
		ended=(action "ytEnded")
	}}
</section>

<p>Multiple players on the same route are supported as well.</p>
